libs.content:
find_library(orc_static_lib
               names orc
               paths ${orc_root}
               no_default_path
               path_suffixes ${arrow_library_path_suffixes})

find_library(re2_lib
               names re2_static
                     re2
                     "${cmake_static_library_prefix}re2${re2_msvc_static_lib_suffix}${cmake_static_library_suffix}"
                     "${cmake_shared_library_prefix}re2${cmake_shared_library_suffix}"
               paths ${re2_root}
               path_suffixes ${arrow_library_path_suffixes}
               no_default_path)

deps.context:
find_package(awssdk ${find_package_args}
             components config
                        s3
                        transfer
                        identity-management
                        sts)
